text: (devanuva): imrange diyaniya vana maryamya. æya tamange pativata araksa kara gattaya. ebævin ehi (maryam vana æyage garbhayehi) apage atmayangen (ek pranayak) pimmbemu. æya tama deviyange ayavanda dharmayanda satyaya kara tæbu atara (deviyanta) sampurnayenma avanata vuvangen keneku vasayenma sitiyaya
